# Machine Learning Integration
- Use Ollama on localhost for LLM classification and embeddings (nomic-embed-text).
- Build a per-account folder index (RAG) from archived messages; classify inbox mail via similar examples + JSON LLM output.
- Process email content efficiently; cap body preview length; sample up to N messages per archive folder (configurable on Training tab, default 10). Avoid a low global index cap that forces only a few samples per folder when many folders are selected.
- Handle Ollama offline errors with clear user messages.